(ms-cli Architecture) Tj
T*
T*
(This document describes the target architecture after the refactor \(see) Tj
T*
(docs/ms-cli-refactor.md\). It is the single contributor-facing) Tj
T*
(architecture reference.) Tj
T*
T*
(Three-Repo Model) Tj
T*
T*
(    ms-cli \(this repo\)          runtime -- TUI, agent loop, tool registry) Tj
T*
(    ms-skills            instructions -- SKILL.md + skill.yaml per skill) Tj
T*
(    ms-factory \(incubating/\)    knowledge -- operator/failure/trick/model cards) Tj
T*
T*
(- ms-cli loads skills from ms-skills and cards from ms-factory.) Tj
T*
(- Skills are portable across CLIs \(Claude Code, OpenCode, Gemini CLI,) Tj
T*
(  Codex\).) Tj
T*
(- Factory cards grow from real experiment data and incident reports.) Tj
T*
T*
(Top-Level Shape) Tj
T*
T*
(    ms-cli/) Tj
T*
(      cmd/ms-cli/              process entrypoint) Tj
T*
(      internal/) Tj
T*
(        app/                   composition root, startup, commands, UI bridging) Tj
T*
(        factory/               local factory card store and resolver) Tj
T*
(        project/               roadmap and weekly status helpers) Tj
T*
(        train/                 train request and target types) Tj
T*
(      agent/) Tj
T*
(        context/               token budget and compaction) Tj
T*
(        loop/                  ReAct-style execution engine \(the core runtime\)) Tj
T*
(        memory/                memory store, retrieval, and policy) Tj
T*
(        session/               session state and persistence) Tj
T*
(      workflow/) Tj
T*
(        train/                 train lane controller, setup, run, demo backend) Tj
T*
(      integrations/) Tj
T*
(        domain/                external domain schema and client) Tj
T*
(        factory/               remote factory fetch and sync) Tj
T*
(        llm/                   provider registry and OpenAI-compatible client) Tj
T*
(        skills/                skill listing, loading, and metadata) Tj
T*
(      permission/              permission policy, types, store) Tj
T*
(      runtime/) Tj
T*
(        shell/                 stateful shell command runner) Tj
T*
(        probes/                local and target readiness probes) Tj
T*
(      tools/) Tj
T*
(        fs/                    read, grep, glob, edit, write tools) Tj
T*
(        shell/                 shell tool wrapper) Tj
T*
(      ui/                      Bubble Tea app, shared model, panels, slash commands) Tj
T*
(      trace/                   execution trace writing) Tj
T*
(      report/                  summary generation) Tj
ET
endstream
