T*
(  \(summaries only\). Loads one skill fully on demand \(SKILL.md +) Tj
T*
(  skill.yaml metadata\).) Tj
T*
T*
(- internal/factory/ Local card store. Search, get, list cards. Status) Tj
T*
(  from pack manifest.) Tj
