T*
(  demo backend. Independent of agent loop -- uses its own event system.) Tj
T*
T*
(- tools/ LLM-callable tool surfaces \(filesystem, shell\). Stateless tool) Tj
T*
(  definitions.) Tj
T*
T*
(- runtime/shell/ Stateful command runner with workspace, timeout, and) Tj
T*
(  safety checks.) Tj
T*
T*
(- permission/ Permission decisions and persistence for sensitive) Tj
T*
(  actions.) Tj
T*
T*
(- ui/ Bubble Tea interface. Consumes events, renders panels. Not) Tj
T*
(  imported by lower layers.) Tj
T*
